                       Bank, ______________ Road, Bangalore.</div><br/>
                    <div style="font-size:17px;text-align:justify;">d. Rs. ________/- (Rupees _________________Only) by way of Demand 
                    Draft Bearing No.__________, dated ___________, drawn at
                    ____________ Bank, ___________ Layout, Bangalore in favour of 
                        _______________________.</div><br/><br/>
                    <div style="font-size:17px;text-align:justify;">2. The First Party cancelled all their rights and obligations arising out of the 
                        said Agreement of sale dated <apex:outputText value="{0, DATE, dd'-'MM'-'yyyy}"><apex:param value="{!Booking__c.Sale_Agreement_Date__c}" /></apex:outputText>;</div><br/>
                    <div style="font-size:17px;text-align:justify;">3. The Parties hereby mutually agree and covenant with each other that 
                    neither party has done, executed or performed any act or deed or thing or 
                    suffered anything to the contrary, or in any way be affected or prejudiced 
                        in title of Schedule A Property.</div> <br/>
                    <div style="font-size:17px;text-align:justify;">4. The parties hereby confirm that they do not have any claims against each 
                        other/s, in future save as mentioned above.</div><br/>
                    <div style="font-size:17px;text-align:justify;">5. No payment/s and/or claim/s, of any nature whatsoever, are pending 
                    and/or payable and/or receivable by and between the parties hereto, save 
                        as mentioned herein.</div> <br/>
                    <div style="font-size:17px;text-align:justify;">6. The FIRST Party represented that the original agreement of sale and the 
                        receipts issued by the second party has to return to the second party.</div>
